import styled from "styled-components"
import Adds from "../comps/Adds"
import Footer from "../comps/Footer"
import Navbar from "../comps/Navbar"
import Newsletter from "../comps/Newsletter"

const Container = styled.div`

`

const Product = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Navbar/>
        <Adds/>
        <Wrapper>
            <ImgContainer>
                <Image src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2068349/pexels-photo-2068349.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1"/>
            </ImgContainer>
            <InfoContainer>
                <Title></Title>
                <Desc>Product description here some nonsense...</Desc>
                <Price>$ 20</Price>
            </InfoContainer>
        </Wrapper>
        <Newsletter/>
        <Footer/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Product
